summary: That Tar-Man guy I posted ages ago, and my other draughr tests.
descriptionHtml:
So, it's not a playable resource but I figured it might be cool to upload this for anyone that wants to use it.

It's the Tar Zombie from Return of the Living Dead, as well as several variants including a low-quality skinned corpse, a burnt body, a creepy oily slim-jim draugr, and a few other oddities.

The ESP places Tar man in I believe Falkreath's Hall of the Dead.
author: The_Funktasm
